  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks @bobylito , I write my code like this but I get error : \r\n\r\n> Uncaught TypeError: Cannot read property 'setQuery' of null\r\n    at InstantSearch.searchFunction [as _searchFunction] (search.js:53)\r\n    at AlgoliaSearchHelper.helper.search (instantsearch.js:13075)\r\n    at InstantSearch.start (instantsearch.js:13089)\r\n    at search.js:423\r\n\r\nmy code : \r\n```\r\nvar searchProduct = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: '...',\r\n  apiKey: '...', // search only API key, no ADMIN key\r\n  indexName: 'market_products'\r\n});\r\n\r\nvar searchShop = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: '...',\r\n  apiKey: '...', // search only API key, no ADMIN key\r\n  indexName: 'market_shops',\r\n  searchFunction: function(helper) {\r\n    var query = searchShop.helper.state.query;\r\n    searchProduct.helper.setQuery(query);\r\n    searchProduct.helper.search();\r\n    helper.search();\r\n  }\r\n});\r\n\r\n\r\n// shared search box2\r\nvar searchBox2 = instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\r\n  container: '#searchBox2',\r\n  placeholder: 'جستجو',\r\n  reset: {\r\n    template:'<img src=\"search/images/greenMultiply2.png\" style=\"position: absolute;top: 20px;width: 25px;height: auto;left: 5px;\" alt=\"\">' }\r\n});\r\n\r\nsearchShop.addWidget(searchBox2);\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhat should I do now?",
